<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Masaru Admin</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; font-family: sans-serif; background: #1a1c1e; color: white; display: flex; }
        .sidebar { width: 240px; background: #2c2f33; height: 100vh; position: fixed; border-right: 1px solid #444; }
        .main { flex: 1; margin-left: 240px; padding: 40px; }
        .card { background: #2f3136; padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #f1c40f; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
        .nav-item { padding: 15px 25px; display: block; color: #b9bbbe; text-decoration: none; }
        .nav-item:hover { background: #3c3f44; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <div style="padding: 25px; font-weight: bold; color: #f1c40f; font-size: 20px;">ADMIN PANEL</div>
        <a href="/profile" class="nav-item">🏠 กลับหน้าโปรไฟล์</a>
        <a href="/admin" class="nav-item" style="background: #3c3f44;">🛠️ ตั้งค่าบอท</a>
        <a href="/logout" class="nav-item" style="color: #ed4245;">🚪 ออกจากระบบ</a>
    </div>
    <div class="main">
        <h1>🛠️ ระบบจัดการหลังบ้าน</h1>
        <div class="card">
            <div style="color: #b9bbbe; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 12px;">จำนวนผู้ใช้ในฐานข้อมูล</div>
            <div style="font-size: 40px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px;"><%= totalUsers %> คน</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>